Package: tidyroc
Title: Calculates ROC and precision-recall curves
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Dariya",
           family = "Sydykova", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dariya.k.sydykova@gmail.com")
Description: This packages calculates necessary values to plot ROC and precision-recall curves. The functions in this package are meant to be integrated with the Tidyverse, specifically, with the packages `broom`, `dplyr`, and `ggplot2`. 
URL: https://github.com/dariyasydykova/tidyroc
